00:02:30.040 --> 00:02:34.670
Other Peoples Clothes is a self portrait photo
series in which artist Caleb Cole selects

00:02:34.670 --> 00:02:37.230
a certain outfit and creates a scene around
it.

00:02:37.230 --> 00:02:41.810
He's interested in what the daily lives of
other people are like and tries to place himself

00:02:41.810 --> 00:02:44.720
in their lives by stepping in their shoes
so to speak.

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:47.210
He has been working on the project for about
5 years.

00:02:47.210 --> 00:02:51.530
Each portrait starts with a particular article
of clothing and he builds the scene around

00:02:51.530 --> 00:02:52.530
it.&nbsp;

